data.description: Retreat to your very own peaceful home in the Riverstone Ranch subdivision. Very well maintained and updated 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage, brick home with in a quiet community, and minutes away from a variety of dining and shopping. Home features an updated kitchen (2021) with granite countertops, updated backsplash, white cabinets, and stainless steel appliances, tile throughout the living areas. Home has a formal dining area enclosed with beautiful sliding double barn doors, which can be alternatively used as an office or den. You'll also find an expansive family room open to the breakfast area and kitchen, high ceilings, recessed lighting, and plenty of natural light. Enjoy tranquil evenings on your covered patio and no back neighbors. New fence installed in 2022. Schedule your showing today!
